author: Brenda Goh
title: Love wins: wedding preparations resume in Wuhan as coronavirus lockdown lifts
description: Peng Jing stifles a laugh as she looks into the eyes of her tuxedo-clad fiancee, Yao Bin, who is in turn trying not to step on the long train of her white wedding dress.
content:
WUHAN, China (Reuters) - Peng Jing stifles a laugh as she looks into the eyes of her tuxedo-clad fiancee, Yao Bin, who is in turn trying not to step on the long train of her white wedding dress. 
“Smile!”, shouts the photographer as he snaps away.
